                             Cellect

   <div class=container>

   <p class=lead>Helps you select data in tables the same way you
   select cells in a spreadsheet.

   It's:

   o  <a href=https://raw.github.com/jablko/cellect/master/cellect.js>
      A JavaScript</a> you can install in your web page,

   o  <a href="javascript:(function(){document.body.appendChild(document.createElement('script')).src='http://code.jquery.com/jquery.min.js';document.body.appendChild(document.createElement('script')).src='https://raw.github.com/jablko/cellect/master/cellect.js'})()">
      A bookmarklet</a> you can run on any page,

   o  A Greasemonkey
      <a href=https://raw.github.com/jablko/cellect/master/greasemonkey/cellect.user.js>
      user script</a> and a
      <a href=https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/cellect/nbcoeiihmfepcagkdeoodgnegkddcpop>
      Chrome extension</a>.


